#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:266
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DJMOD_OPERATIVE_DIES\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"So.\" Your new but already dying crew's face is dead serious. \"Since you "
"paid for me... you must be looking for... our special kind of goods, "
"right?\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:270
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DJMOD_OPERATIVE_DIES\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_NO_COORDS_NO_VISIT_RADIKAL_SECTOR\"]/text"
msgstr "...Sure, why not?"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:272
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DJMOD_OPERATIVE_DIES\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_NO_COORDS_NO_VISIT_RADIKAL_SECTOR\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"He's clearly struggling to speak. \"Then... make your way there, loaded with all the scr-... Ugh. All the scrap you can find... to fund progress. You'll find your way. M-... my mission is over.\" He hands you some hidden sector's coordinates, then dies.\n"
"\t\t\tYou notice he was already gravely injured and only held on until he could deliver this to somebody, fooling both the store owner and yourself. Some valuable tech in his pocket helps you recoup your losses. \n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tMaybe you'll find out what that was all about the next time you reroute in hyperspeed..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:282
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DJMOD_OPERATIVE_DIES\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_NO_COORDS_NO_VISIT_RADIKAL_SECTOR\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr ""
"Curious dedication, for what looks like nothing more than a black market "
"advert."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:289
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DJMOD_OPERATIVE_DIES\"]/choice[@req=\"visited_radikal_sector\"]/text"
msgstr "We've already visited the RadiKal sector. Rest in peace, soldier."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:291
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DJMOD_OPERATIVE_DIES\"]/choice[@req=\"visited_radikal_sector\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Progress sha- shall continue... this does bring me comfort... Thank you.\" He dies with a faint smile on his face.\n"
"\t\t\tAs usual this agent had an incurable disease and volunteered to spread awareness for RK funding and recruit reckless captains, so you're not surprised. You proceed to loot his valuable tech and dispose of the body."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:298
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DJMOD_OPERATIVE_DIES\"]/choice[@req=\"visited_radikal_sector\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:305
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DJMOD_OPERATIVE_DIES\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "What? Of course not. Wait, are you OK?"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:307
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DJMOD_OPERATIVE_DIES\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"I... ha-... have failed.\" Looking mortified, he crushes a small chip inscribed with a couple capital letters, which briefly but intensely burns. Then he dies.\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\tYou proceed to strip the body, notice the swelling and necrosis, and wonder why selling you illegal gear mattered more to that guy more than his impending death. You wonder if the store owner knew and just scammed you.\n"
"\t\t\tAt least there's some valuable tech in the dead soldier's pocket to recoup your losses."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:316
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DJMOD_OPERATIVE_DIES\"]/choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr ""
"There are surely other ways to revisit this mystery and get to wherever it "
"was going. Moving on."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:360
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_EVENT_STORE_RADIKAL\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"Your sensors stop functioning and your view is suddenly obscured, but apparently that's just the doing of a very cautious and well-equipped band of traders. No wonder, with all the shady business going on around here.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\t[Warning: Limited purchases]"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:363
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_EVENT_STORE_RADIKAL\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"You can't see any shop in the vicinity, but soon a drone from a very well camouflaged ship takes your order.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\t[Warning: Limited purchases]"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:366
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_EVENT_STORE_RADIKAL\"]/text[3]"
msgstr ""
"You are quickly scanned and told to stay right here while the owner of a shop that's too far to see arranges remote delivery of your purchases.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\t[Warning: Limited purchases]"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:369
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_EVENT_STORE_RADIKAL\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"While you wait at the trading spot, a tiny drone entertains you with an endless feed of funny videos.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\t[Warning: Limited purchases]"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:372
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_EVENT_STORE_RADIKAL\"]/text[5]"
msgstr ""
"You are forced to leave your ship parked outside while you do your shopping closely escorted inside what looked like a random asteroid.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\t[Warning: Limited purchases]"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:375
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_EVENT_STORE_RADIKAL\"]/text[6]"
msgstr ""
"The clerk here is very quiet. Once you install the goods in your ship, as per the deal you wipe recent records so that the merchant's ship appears to have never been here at all.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\t[Warning: Limited purchases]"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:378
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_EVENT_STORE_RADIKAL\"]/text[7]"
msgstr ""
"You reluctantly agree to leave your ship in an empty space matrix before they grant you access to the store, and when you exit it, there is no other ship but yours here.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\t[Warning: Limited purchases]"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:389
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_ENSLAVED\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Slavers are quite comfortably installed in this sector, in great part due to"
" the lack of regulation. You stumble upon one."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:392
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_ENSLAVED\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "See who they might have for sale."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:394
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_ENSLAVED\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Feds here? You're surely in need of some muscle, and this might just be "
"your lucky day! We have an elite warrior to do the heavy lifting for you, "
"greatly discounted because we must trade fast and leave for... reasons. What"
" say you?\" You notice that the discount is pretty solid indeed, maybe too "
"good."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:396
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_ENSLAVED\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Purchase the elite slave."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:398
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_ENSLAVED\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "You hand over the scrap to the slavers..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:404
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_ENSLAVED\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:410
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_ENSLAVED\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
